Recommended Uses For Product
Office, School, TV Cabinet, Indoor
  • SURGE PROTECTION: Our protectors ensure that your TV and appliances are safeguarded from high voltage and low voltage, power interruptions, peak currents, surges, blackouts, voltage fluctuations, and load variations. They prolong the lifespan of your devices and reduce maintenance costs.
  • DUAL OUTLETS: Our protectors feature two outlets, offering simultaneous protection for two appliances. It's not just limited to TVs; it's compatible with various appliances like refrigerators, microwaves, water dispensers, washing machines, dishwashers, and more. This enhances convenience while avoiding the expense of purchasing additional protectors.
  • CLEAR INDICATOR LIGHTS: Our protectors come with simple indicator lights for normal, high voltage, low voltage, and delay states. If the power voltage exceeds the safety range, it will automatically cut off power, and the corresponding indicator light will activate. This allows you to immediately and clearly understand current protection and voltage status.
  • SMART 3-MINUTE DELAY: Following voltage fluctuations, our protectors include a smart 3-minute delay. This ensures reconnection only when the power is completely stable. This feature prevents your devices from repeatedly turning on and off during voltage changes and protects them from potential power surges when power is restored after a blackout.
  • USER-FRIENDLY: Designed for plug-and-play, installation is very simple. Once plugged in, it occupies minimal space and won't interfere with the normal use of other outlets.

Product description

Power surges can not only destroy your TV, it can also start an electrical fire.

A strong power surge can cause an arcing of electrical current in your TV, especially those with microprocessors and inverter boards are susceptible to damage as strong power surges can fry these parts and even melt some of the plastic parts away.

While weak power surges don’t ruin your TV outright, it can build incremental damage to your TV, affecting its performance and shortening its lifespan overtime.

So a high quality surge protector for appliances is a must-have item in all homes!


This surge protector is smart enough to constantly sense the voltage fluctuations in the electric line. If there’s any fluctuation it will automatically turn off the power supply and prevent your TV from getting damaged. Once the power returns to normal, there is a 3 minutes time delay to confirm that the voltage is stable, so that it could auto re-connect power for your TV.


The failure detection time is only 0.5 seconds, which means our voltage protector will respond rapidly once a voltage fluctuation is detected. It provides the most professional protection for your TV, so you can be more reassuring of using it.


Two installation methods are offered, you can use screws to fix, or use strong nano-markless hook sticker to attach directly to the wall. The installation is extremely flexible, after plugging in the power supply, it does not occupy the space nor affect the use of other sockets.

In this modern world that we live in, power surges and transients are everywhere. Although we can’t predict when will happen, we can be prepared for them, protect your expensive electronics with a surge protector!
